---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Experiencias Exclusivas">
  <section class="relative min-h-screen text-white flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden pt-20" style="background-color: #0b0707;">
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 flex flex-col items-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="font-sans text-[#C5A059] tracking-[0.4em] text-[10px] md:text-[12px] uppercase mb-6">Momentos de Alta Gama</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl text-white mb-8 tracking-wide uppercase font-premium leading-tight">
        Experiencias <br/><span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-[#C5A059] to-white">Multisensoriales</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="h-[1px] w-20 bg-[#C5A059]/40 mb-8"></div>
      <p class="font-sans text-white/70 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed tracking-wide mb-12 max-w-xl">
        Diseñamos eventos privados, catas exclusivas y talleres de personalización donde el lujo se siente a través de cada uno de los sentidos.
      </p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/51953435738" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-12 py-4 border border-[#C5A059] overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-[#C5A059]">
        <span class="relative z-10 font-sans text-[10px] tracking-widest text-[#C5A059] group-hover:text-black uppercase">Reservar Experiencia VIP</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>